    <ul class="links inline"><li class="comment_comments first"><a href="../tech/drupal/drupal-views-ui-filter-fields-content-type.html#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting.">2 comments</a></li>
<li class="node_read_more"><a href="../tech/drupal/drupal-views-ui-filter-fields-content-type.html" title="Read the rest of Drupal Views UI Filter Fields by Content Type.">Read more</a></li>
